

                To run and build that project with older JDK version
                ----------------------------------------------------


login as root and execute the following :

# update-alternatives --config java

select the desired java version

then

as user
$ export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun-1.6.0.26

to reverse :

# update-alternatives --config java

select the desired java version

then

export JAVA_HOME=/opt/jdk1.7.0_25



